            ],
            "stanza_text": "Bien qu’elle soit ta meilleure amie,\nC’est farce ce que nous la trompons\nJusques à l’excès, sans penser mie\nA elle, tant nos instants sont bons,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [],
            "stanza_text": ""
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Je fais des comparaisons, de même",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "9",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Toi cocufiant ton autre amant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Et je dois dire que ton système",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4−5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Pour le cocufier est charmant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "9",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je fais des comparaisons, de même\nToi cocufiant ton autre amant,\nEt je dois dire que ton système\nPour le cocufier est charmant,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [],
            "stanza_text": ""
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Mon plaisir est d’autant plus coupable",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "(Et plus exquis, grâce à ton concours)",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Qu’elle se montre aussi très capable",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Et fort experte aux choses d’amours,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mon plaisir est d’autant plus coupable\n(Et plus exquis, grâce à ton concours)\nQu’elle se montre aussi très capable\nEt fort experte aux choses d’amours,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [],
            "stanza_text": ""
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Trompons-la bien, car elle nous trompe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Peut-être aussi, tant on est coquins",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Et qu’il n’est de pacte qu’on ne rompe.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+4",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Trompons-les bien. Nuls remords mesquins !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Trompons-la bien, car elle nous trompe\nPeut-être aussi, tant on est coquins\nEt qu’il n’est de pacte qu’on ne rompe.\nTrompons-les bien. Nuls remords mesquins !"
        },
